 Carriers in Cyber Security :-
                             * SOC Analyst (David): who monitor the attack happening
                               in real time i.e see the malicious attack

                             * Pentester  (Maya) : Tells how a attacker got in the
                                system after attack happen i.e Tell the sequence
                                 of attack
                                  . Email sent
                                  . Attack triggered
                                  . Control Taken
                                  . Data Stolen
                             * Forensic Analyst (Priya): Investigate about the attack
                                   see on which time which step of hacking held

                             * Security Engineer (Sam) : Lock the door so this attack
                               can not happen again i.e He will block unauthorized
                               access and allow only office work processes

